description:
Track your calorie intake - Completely offline!
Easily track your eating habits

Never suffer another ad while logging your foods.
FitBook is completely Free and Open Source. 
Have confidence we won't be marketing
to you or sharing your data with third parties.
Everything is stored locally - that means internet
connectivity is optional.

If you notice any bugs feel free to open a ticket at
https://github.com/brandonp2412/FitBook
